data.description: Welcome to luxury living at Barnsley Park! This upscale home offers great attention to detail and craftsmanship, making it a must-see for those seeking the finest in home living. Pull into the convenience of a two-car garage on the main level, setting the tone for the elegance that awaits inside. Stepping through the door, you're greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly integrates a charming family room with a fireplace, a spacious dining area, and a kitchen that's a chef's dream. The kitchen  features custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, high-end stainless steel appliances, a central island, and a pantry for optimal organization. The main level also hosts a well-appointed powder room and laundry room, strategically connected to the master closet for added functionality. Experience the luxury master suite, strategically positioned at the rear of the home for privacy and tranquility. The master bath is a haven of relaxation, offering a generously-sized tiled shower, a freestanding tub, double vanities, and a separate toilet room. The master closet is a standout feature, custom-built shelving for an organized wardrobe.Venture to the second level, where three bedrooms and two full bathrooms await. Two bedrooms feature walk-in closets, while one impresses with both a walk-in closet and additional storage space which can be finished out for additional living space. Hardwood floors throughout the home, with tiled surfaces in the laundry room and master bath. Ascend the hardwood stairs to find plush comfort with carpeted bedrooms on the upper level.
